hackathon-description-text: hackGSU is the inaugural Hackathon hosted by the GSU Computer Science Department's ACM & IEEE student organizations. 100% free of charge, Lots of Food, $$ Prizes $$ This year, hackGSU will be a 300+ participant event taking place from March 25th-27th.
hackathon-eligibility: All university students! You do not have to be a computer science major to participate in the competition! If you're someone who is willing to learn and wants to take a shot at changing the world, no matter what your field is, you definitely belong here.
